              },
              "free_text": [
                " reported systematic uncertainty",
                "The following contributions to the uncertainty budget",
                "were considered: target mass, impurities, detector",
                "efficiency, half-lives, time measurement, dead-time,",
                "Faraday cup efficiency, and beam characteristics. The",
                "two major source of uncertainty were:"
